<script>
    export default {
        name: 'AddIcon',
        props:{
            size:{
                type:String,
                require:false
            },
            color:{
                type:String,
                require:false
            }
        },
        data(){
            return{
                IconSize:null,
                IconColor:null,
            }
        },
        mounted(){
            this.getSize();
            this.getColor();
        },
        methods:{
            getSize(){
                if (this.$props.size){
                    this.IconSize=this.$props.size
                    return
                }
                this.IconSize="30px"
                return
            },
            getColor(){
                if (this.$props.color){
                    this.IconColor=this.$props.color
                    return
                }
                this.IconColor="#000000"
                return
            },
            AddPost(){
                this.$emit("AddPost")
            }
        },
    }
</script>
